"},{"pid":"954218e8486dfec872783ae31125660adcf2f1d5","tid":659284,"uid":169310,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T19:40:03.000Z","msg":"去台灣求其搵個STEM台仔都整到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 40萬有找，仲要係台紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 港共真係貪到出曬面"},{"pid":"c73db2d4d77ee99b6ad5f58f0246097f7b63792e","tid":659284,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ace22c38e7b2437dcf7280cbd290ade17cddb12d","tid":659284,"uid":88134,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"fe73c06007d3241490b1c264c640cf918945287c","tid":659284,"uid":83582,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T17:10:12.000Z","msg":"老人家用埋o的垃圾山寨機, 點玩呀? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T19:29:18.000Z","msg":"其實佢地用勁機定廢機都唔會同你玩呢d<br />\n得閒無野做同個孫仔孫女玩下唔好？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T20:59:38.000Z","msg":"我起另外個貼都講，佢係咪以為個個都用唉瘋實或S9+<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a20a859d3f385a7d74b40025e51add6fa44e12cc","tid":659284,"uid":77189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T07:57:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c98fe8ce0ecf8d1e3843465a018948c2168b55","tid":659284,"uid":128603,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T09:40:27.000Z","msg":"利益輸送常見的手段：<br />\n<br />\n    &bull; 綁標，以不公正的技術標，榜定特定廠商才有投標資格。<br />\n    &bull; 圍標。<br />\n    &bull; 以過於低廉的價格，將公有財產販售/出租給私人或財團，不過在某些情況下這種利益輸送是合乎道德的，例如政府免費提供土地甚至補貼給鐵道公司，因為鐵道公司幾乎有高額虧本，但是鐵道可以大幅減少社會成本及政府支出；在臺灣，官員將其稱為肥肉配瘦肉（為了讓公司做對社會有利的虧本生意，給他一些好賺的生意補償），而高雄捷運的虧損就是政府給予利益過少的例子。<br />\n    &bull; 指定廠商議價。<br />\n    &bull; 先低價搶標，後再追加預算。<br />\n    &bull; 收買評審委員。<br />\n    &bull; 透漏底標給投標廠商。<br />\n    &bull; 使用基金會轉移資產。<br />\n    &bull; 將藝術性的設計圖或表演指定給自己人承接，但價格過高或成品缺乏藝術價值；這是因為藝術有難以估價比較、不能以傳統方式競標的特性，相關法令會特別寬鬆，這可以合法將大筆公帑（而非合理報酬）送給自己人。<br />\n    &bull; 政府持有的基金在進出股市交易前，先行洩漏交易相關資訊，也就是報明牌，供他人短線炒作。<br />\n    &bull; 有些法律會阻擋特定人物的不當利益而產生公共利益，民代因為自身因素而阻擋這種法案也是利益輸送，例如自家開工廠的立委阻擋更嚴格的排放及噪音法案，吸煙立委阻擋擴大禁煙範圍的法案，仍算是廣義的貪污。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%88%A9%E7%9B%8A%E8%BC%B8%E9%80%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%2588%25A9%25E7%259B%258A%25E8%25BC%25B8%25E9%2580%2581&d=wapzj4paykHaBJyKCXJ%2FoQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=752217de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%88%A9%E7%9B%8A%E8%BC%B8%E9%80%81</a>"},{"pid":"afed558f43f6ccc8c66677b2581b7bd058ce2a04","tid":659284,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T09:41:03.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"fbbb45628eabe25c661730ddf9d560c7b57bfb81","tid":659284,"uid":118120,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T09:42:53.000Z","msg":"四百萬應該夠開發一隻大廠既中型遊戲喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a93ebb47854380d42589a72ef9bcd38bb95910","tid":659284,"uid":77189,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fbbb45628eabe25c661730ddf9d560c7b57bfb81","tid":659284,"uid":118120,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T09:42:53.000Z","msg":"四百萬應該夠開發一隻大廠既中型遊戲喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T10:33:22.000Z","msg":"依家明顯驚死你班港豬唔知佢利益輸送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e294e2c5e58082a5feb8701ef91c8947fe8db17c","tid":659284,"uid":77189,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f8a93ebb47854380d42589a72ef9bcd38bb95910","tid":659284,"uid":77189,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fbbb45628eabe25c661730ddf9d560c7b57bfb81","tid":659284,"uid":118120,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T09:42:53.000Z","msg":"四百萬應該夠開發一隻大廠既中型遊戲喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyT