:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開發者Animoca Brands發言人Ibrahim El-Mouelhy則表示，「八段錦健康遊戲」並非外界所想如此簡單，形容網民在未知詳細計畫前就批評成本過高，是「completely ignorant」（完全無知）。他指，該app會有虛擬教練教長者做八段錦，將有<span style=\"color: red;\">實時分析及反饋（feedback）</span>功能。透過手機鏡頭，程式可實時了解及以語音矯正動作。他指，科技門檻高、背後技術複雜，400萬不是一個誇張數字。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一見到real time feedback依個功能,<br />\n即刻令我諗起曾經聽過UST有份FYP係做有關學太極嘅程式, 又係有real time feedback<br />\n<br />\n於是我去google search, 屌你第一個就搵到<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cse.ust.hk/ug/fyp/bestfyp/2013-2014/MA2_Poster.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cse.ust.hk%2Fug%2Ffyp%2Fbestfyp%2F2013-2014%2FMA2_Poster.pdf&d=wapzj4paykHaBJyKCXJ%2FoQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=34b08220\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cse.ust.hk/ug/fyp/bestfyp/2013-2014/MA2_Poster.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n人地一年就做到嘅野, 你只係移植去手機度,<br />\n你用三年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要452萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> WTF<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T16:33:03.000Z","msg":"八段錦GE野你唔明GA啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T16:35:01.000Z","msg":"我沙田舞王日日落機舖跳八段錦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T18:40:41.000Z","msg":"開心又關你叉事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}